-- Safaricom's CEO Joseph Doesn't See His Imminent Departure Affecting Shares
-- Eric Ombok
-- 2010-07-23T05:20:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-23/safaricom-s-ceo-joseph-doesn-t-see-his-imminent-departure-affecting-shares.html

          
          
             Safaricom Ltd.’s Chief Executive
Officer, Michael Joseph, said he doesnt expect his resignation,
announced yesterday, to affect the company’s share price as his
departure was expected.  
 The company’s shares, which closed trade in Nairobi
yesterday at 5.7 shillings, may rise as high as 6.8 shillings,
he said in an interview on Kenya Television Network, which is
based in the city, without giving a timeframe.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Eric Ombok in Nairobi at 
 eombok@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        